{"id":"api/router/RouterLinkActive","title":"RouterLinkActive","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router/RouterLinkActive\", \"name\": \"RouterLinkActive\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts#L33-L258\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"routerlinkactive\">RouterLinkActive<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#routerlinkactive\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8cq1twm5vj7uk1bv29yxmeo9p\">跟踪元素上的链接路由当前是否处于活动状态，并允许你指定一个或多个 CSS\n类，以便在链接路由处于活动状态时添加到该元素。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/router/RouterModule\">\n      <code>RouterModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"links\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">links</span>: <a href=\"api/core/QueryList\" class=\"code-anchor\">QueryList</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLink</a>&gt;</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"isActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">isActive</span></code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">只读</span>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"routerLinkActiveOptions\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">routerLinkActiveOptions</span>: {\n    exact: boolean;\n} | <a href=\"api/router/IsActiveMatchOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">IsActiveMatchOptions</a></code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3mdjkuz153sermohtjc4lgx6m\">用于配置如何确定路由器链接是否处于活动状态的选项。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5skltlbcrc4ykijjnph2ishkp\">参见:</p>\n\n          <p>参见：</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"api/router/Router#isActive\"><code>Router#isActive</code></a>\n</li>\n          </ul>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ariaCurrentWhenActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">ariaCurrentWhenActive</span>?: 'page' | 'step' | 'location' | 'date' | 'time' | true | false</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"86bles9nu2kv7epx829w93u0v\">路由器链接处于活动状态时要应用的 Aria-current 属性。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1u0nbf4mwrbm5dx5rc5bho06h\">可能的值：\n<code>'page'</code> | \n<code>'step'</code> | \n<code>'location'</code> | \n<code>'date'</code> | \n<code>'time'</code> | \n<code>true</code> | \n<code>false</code>。</p>\n\n          <p>参见：</p>\n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-current\">aria-current</a>\n</li>\n          </ul>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"isActiveChange\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Output\" class=\"code-anchor\">Output</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">isActiveChange</span>: <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>&lt;boolean&gt;</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">只读</span>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7syabks3mac58er7w5bl52lzg\">你可以用输出 <code>isActiveChange</code> 来在每次链接变为活动或非活动时获取通知。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"76i7ubnx0n9qaaogf4tbyqzv\">发出：true -&gt; 路由处于活动状态 false -&gt; 路由处于非活动状态</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a\n <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\"\n <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\"\n (isActiveChange)=\"this.onRouterLinkActive($event)\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"routerLinkActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a></span>: string | string[]</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"write-only-property\">只写</span>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"export-as\">\n  <h2 id=\"template-variable-references\">模板变量参考手册<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#template-variable-references\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table export-as-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>标识符</th>\n        <th>用途</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"export-as\">\n        <td><code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a></code></td>\n        <td><code>#myTemplateVar=\"<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>\"</code></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"786goryyu5vyqa3yzsxmledvd\">使用此指令为与活动路径关联的元素创建视觉差异。比如，以下代码会在路由器激活关联的路由时突出显示单词 “Bob”：</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"atjlq12kbgsrn3el8qxltmw01\">你可以设置一个或多个类，比如：</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dlumaue5zu160i6rjyk8xv60o\">你可以设置一个或多个类，比如：</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"class1 class2\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" [<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>]=\"['class1', 'class2']\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bnm1eitl63jib1z92dbmyd8yr\">你可以通过传入 <code>exact: true</code> 来配置 RouterLinkActive。这样，只有当 url 和此链接精确匹配时才会添加这些类。</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\" [routerLinkActiveOptions]=\"{exact:\ntrue}\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bgpmnmpciggsqvwzrhdzksqvi\">要直接检查 <code>isActive</code> 状态，请将 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> 实例分配给模板变量。比如，以下代码会在不分配任何 CSS 类的情况下检查状态：</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a> #rla=\"<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>\"&gt;\n  Bob {{ rla.isActive ? '(already open)' : ''}}\n&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2786m9jwnd10qxsb2fyf3q5xg\">最后，你还可以把 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> 指令用在 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLink</a></code> 的各级祖先节点上。</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;div <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\" [routerLinkActiveOptions]=\"{exact: true}\"&gt;\n  &lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/jim\"&gt;Jim&lt;/a&gt;\n  &lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"80tqypp7gg14rxp228mzhahk6\"><code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> 指令也可用于设置 aria-current 属性，以为视障用户提供活动元素的另一种区别。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"49ay8bv68t6a8uebdmnr6tt9r\">例如，以下代码在确实处于活动状态时将 'active' 类添加到主页链接，并在这种情况下将其 aria-current\n属性设置为 'page'：</p>\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active\" ariaCurrentWhenActive=\"page\"&gt;Home Page&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n    \n  </section>\n\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/OnChanges\n - api/core/OnDestroy\n - api/router\n - api/router/RouterModule\n - guide/accessibility\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/router\n - guide/router-reference\n - guide/router-tutorial\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/EventEmitter\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/Output\n - api/core/QueryList\n - api/router\n - api/router/IsActiveMatchOptions\n - api/router/Router#isActive\n - api/router/RouterLink\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#instance-properties\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#routerlinkactive\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#selectors\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#template-variable-references\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#导出自\n - api/router/RouterModule\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-current\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts#L33-L258\n-->"}